  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div xml:id="Kali19-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">itu pirivuṇarttappaṭṭa tōḻi celavu vilakkavum piriviṉmēṟ ceṉṟa uḷḷattaṉāyiṉāṉai 
            nī piriyiṉ ivaḷ iṟantupaṭumeṉac colliya vāypāṭṭāṉ maṟuttatu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"/>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="Kali19">
            <lg type="edition">
                <l>cevviya tīviya colli yavaṟṟoṭu </l>
                <l>paiya muyaṅkiya vaññāṉ ṟavaiyellām</l>
                <l>poyyātal yāṉyāṅ kaṟikōmaṟ ṟaiya</l>
                <l>vakaṉakar koḷḷā valartalait tantu</l>
                <l>pakaṉmuṉi veñcura muḷḷa laṟintēṉ</l>
                <l>makaṉallai maṉṟa viṉi;</l>
                <l rend="space">celliṉic ceṉṟunī ceyyum viṉaimuṟṟi</l>
                <l>yaṉpaṟa māṟiyā muḷḷat tuṟantavaḷ</l>
                <l>paṇpu maṟitirō veṉṟu varuvārai</l>
                <l>yeṉṟiṟam yātum viṉaval viṉaviṟ</l>
                <l>pakaliṉ viḷaṅkuniṉ cemmal citaiyat</l>
                <l>tavalaruñ ceyviṉai muṟṟāma lāṇṭō</l>
                <l>ravalam paṭutalu muṇṭu.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>            “That day when, speaking straight [and] sweet words</l>
<l corresp="1-2c">[and] with those gently embracing [me], </l>
<l corresp="2d-3">how could I know that all those were lies, lord? </l>
<l corresp="4">That, bringing gossip that would not reach the wide mansion, </l>
<l corresp="5">[you] would think of the hot desert hateful by midday I knew. </l>
<l corresp="6">Indeed, you are no man. Now, </l>
<l rend="space" corresp="7">go now. Having gone, completing the work you do, </l>
<l>without love, changing, would you know the quality</l>
<l>of here whom you abandoned, while we remember [your]?” so saying, (8-9c)  </l>
<l corresp="9d-10">don’t ask those who come on my account anything. If you ask, </l>
<l>without completing the work to do that is difficult to fail, (12) </l>
<l corresp="11">so that you superiority that shines like the day is laid waste, </l>
<l>there is unique suffering to be undergone.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
